#!/usr/bin/env -S python3 -u
"""
ticket-bot: Slack-driven ticket solver

Uses Socket Mode (WebSocket) to receive events in real time.
Responds to DMs directly, and to @mentions in channels.

Handles:
  - "UB-1234" → starts ticket-solve
  - "UB-1234 https://slack.com/..." → starts with Slack context
  - "UB-1234 extra context here" → starts with extra context
  - Thread replies on completed jobs → resumes Claude session with feedback

Run:  ticket-bot
Stop: Ctrl+C
"""

